  "text": "To determine titin isoform expression in both WT and HM TA muscle, TA homogenate samples were suspended in SDS sample buffer and underwent electrophoresis using vertical SDS agarose gels designed for high molecular weight protein separation as described previously [CITATION_1] . Additionally, to assess the lower molecular weight myofilament protein isoform expression, homogenates samples were separated using standard SDS-PAGE (12%) [CITATION_2] ; gels were stained with Coomassie blue.",
